title: Cabeza de Dragon
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben hacer funcionar un estacionamiento secreto en su terraza para poder darse una ducha.

title: Blankie
description: It's bedtime and Bing's getting ready for bed. But what will he do when his blankie gets wet in the toilet?

title: Fashion Forward
description: When the Fashionistas launch a new line of brainwashing clothing, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop the fashion trend before it's too late.

title: Falafel's in Jail
description: Falafel's in trouble with the law despite pleading his innocence. Apple and Onion vow to break him out.

title: Schnorp
description: The Thunderkittens plug a new video game cartridge into Snarf only to learn that it didn't load a game, it loaded a whole new personality into their pal! Meet Schnorp, a kind Swedish man who loves the beauty of nature and collecting berries! Schnorp is loads of fun, but we're gonna want Snarf back, right?

title: Action News
description: Dynamite Watkins has to go extreme lengths breaking a new story.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: Prepare for the Worst
description: Axel and Bobbie Blobby skip out on Sarge's disaster-prep drills, leaving enough of a gap in the team's defenses for a crow to swoop in and snatch Sarge! Feeling responsible, Axel leads the team on a search-and-rescue mission.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Bedtime
description: It's Pocoyo and Pato's bedtime but Pocoyo isn't tired. Every time Pato is just about to fall asleep, he is disturbed by Pocoyo. Eventually Pocoyo is tired out too and together we help Pato drift off to sleep at last.

title: Swimming Pool
description: Bing, Sula and Flop are going to the Swimming Pool, but what will they do when they find that there's no water in the pool?

title: Mush-Mush the Predictor
description: Mush-Mush can't figure out why his sense foot keeps buzzing like crazy until an earthquake shakes the forest. Mush-Mush is sure he predicted it! Convinced he can now predict the future, Mush-Mush starts making predictions for everyone in Mushton.

title: Pizza Hero
description: It's the end of the school year, and as is tradition at Aberdale Elementary, Papa Marianio is slated to dish out his famous pizza along with a spectacle of song and dance. As the kids wait in excitement, they share memories about times with Papa.

title: The Hug
description: When Darwin taunts Gumball about how predictable he is, Gumball tries to prove he can still surprise his buddy. He thinks greeting a kid he barely knows with a hug will do the trick. He's right but doesn't see the awkward social repercussions of the hug coming.

title: Inventor Mentor
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to Italy to help a young girl who wants to be a great inventor.

title: El Futuro
description: Steven por fin está listo para avanzar.

title: Something for Everyone/Skating Lessons/Caillou Becomes a Waiter/Sticking to It!/New Clothes
description: When the park is closed for the day, Caillou's friends come over to his house to play./When Mom drives Sarah to her skating lesson, Caillou decides he wants to take skating lessons too!/When Mom and Dad are getting ready to go out to a restaurant, Caillou doesn't understand why he can't go too!/When Caillou accidentally breaks one of his toys because his room is a mess, Mom suggests a way to make cleaning up fun./When Caillou dresses himself, he learns it's okay to change from your favorite shorts when you find out it's cold outside.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Motel
description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Winning at Whining
description: Vambre's challenge to Prohyas: Don't whine for the entirety of the next mission and you can have the Magisword we get at the end.

title: Ataque en el Palacio de los Panqueques
description: Cuando Gwen se inscribe en un concurso de comer panqueques en el mundialmente famoso Palacio de los Panqueques, Ben encuentra a los Bugg Bros. y debe detenerlos antes de que puedan obtener una provisión infinita del elemento que les da vida a sus creaciones: los panqueques del Palacio del Panqueque.

title: Charlie Ball
description: After Panda gets injured on the basketball court, the Bears invite Charlie to be on their basketball team. But when Charlie gets too good, he starts to ruin all the fun of the game.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Expreso De Gran Estres
description: Durante una transmisión en vivo del nuevo tren bala transcontinental, La Grange se cuela para ganarle al tren. Pero Ben se suma a la diversión, iy no se detendrá ante nada para salir victorioso!

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Lad & Logic
description: KO learns the story of how Mr. Logic came to the plaza.

title: #TrianguloDeOdio
description: Cuando la exnovia de Hal aparece en el partido de bienvenida de la preparatoria Metrópolis y se enfurece por amor, convertida en la villana Star Sapphire, Jessica comienza a cuestionar sus propias tácticas no violentas.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Aluxes
description: When Vic finds an ancient relic that summons a gang of mischievous creatures, he uses them to do his bidding, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fiesta Day
description: The Bears party it up with a living piñatas for Fiesta Day. Wanting the festivities to never end, Grizz wishes for it to be Fiesta Day everyday.

title: Wednesday - Part 4
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Ninja Contra Lava
description: Los ninja se encuentran atrapados en una pirámide y deben escapar de la lava invasora para advertir a la ciudad de NINJAGO de una nueva invasión serpentina.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Road Trippin'
description: Realizing her and the Professor don't have much in common, Bubbles schedules a road trip with just the two of them.

title: Easter Creeps
description: It's Easter and the Tooth Fairy is trying to take over the holiday.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Rock Show
description: Chad's band Dogmon, plays a show for the first time in years, giving Clarence and Mary a chance to really rock out.

title: Bichos
description: Cuando Unikitty y la banda descubren un bicho asqueroso en el castillo, están desesperados por deshacerse de él para siempre, pero Unikitty se niega a permitir que lo aplasten, no importa qué tan asqueroso o peligroso parezca. ¿Qué tipo de red está tejiendo Unikitty para sus amigos?

title: Historia Antigua
description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

title: La Super Increible Aventura en Balsa
description: Unikitty y Hawkodile están "perdidos en el mar," varados en una balsa juntos. Hawkodile ve esto como una oportunidad para mostrarle a Unikitty que está preparado para cualquier cosa con sus habilidades de experto en supervivencia, pero para su sorpresa, todos sus planes fracasan, mientras que la tonta postura de Unikitty de "todo saldrá bien, vamos a divertirnos" está funcionando de una manera genial. ¿Será Hawkodile capaz de soltar su exceso de preparación para salvarlos a ambos, o acaso la diversión caprichosa de Unikitty será su perdición?

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Supply Mom
description: When Chef's mom becomes the supply teacher for a day Duncan replaces Chef's to-do list with one of his own.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: Sword Heist
description: When a local sword shop sells an ultra powerful sword to Ratar-O, Lion-O decides he has to steal it before Ratar-O can come pick it up. Unfortunately Lion-O is completely against stealing, but luckily he knows someone who loves to steal, Lion-S!

title: Winner Takes All
description: After months of training for Luchador Day, Axel needs Masko to coach him against a pair of uninvited competitors - Madcap and Dynamo!

title: Exercising the Demons
description: When a severe screen addiction turns the kids into lazy deadbeats, Chef brings in a professional to whip them into shape.

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Escape from Family Dinner
description: There's a huge water balloon fight at the creek but Craig is stuck at home for a family dinner, unless he can escape.

title: Conquista de Popularidad
description: Cuando Mao Mao descubre que no es tan popular como Colosal y Adorabat, sus amigos deciden reinventarlo en forma de un héroe más amable y tierno.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Enfermo
description: Cuando Mao Mao no quiere reconocer que está enfermo, pone al pueblo en peligro.

title: The Big Sleep
description: When the Professor's latest invention wreaks havoc in the house, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls to stop it before it escapes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Feria de ciencias misteriosas 201x
description: K.O. ayuda a Dendy con su proyecto para feria de ciencias.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Sigue la corriente
description: Cuando Sal se queda en lo de Vic y Val, los chicos no lo soportan como compañero, pero finalmente descubren lo genial y mágico que es.

title: King of the Machines
description: Panthro gets insecure when he finds out Barbastella has a history of dating royalty, so he tries to impress her by becoming "King of the Machines" and giving all the appliances in the Cats' Lair artificial intelligence.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Appleoni
description: The wrong person is getting credit for a new dance craze.

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: Talkie Taxi
description: Bing and Sula discover a new toy at Amma's creche - Talkie Taxi. What will they do when they discover the taxi talks a lot?

title: Giggle Bug
description: When Pocoyo is down in the dumps, Octopus cheers him up. Elly falls over doing her latest dance routine and Octopus cheers her up too. Finally Pato is in a bad mood, and Octopus has to work really hard to get him to giggle.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Assault on Pancake Palace
description: When Gwen enters a pancake eating contest at the world famous Pancake Palace, Ben finds the Bugg Bros. and must stop them before they obtain an endless supply of what fuels their creations: Pancake Palace pancakes.

title: Desde las Profundidades
description: iAxel hace malabares cuidando a Luka y defendiendo la casa de la última abominación del Dr. Nautilus, un monstruo tentáculo que ataca desde cada drenaje, tubería y grifo del edificio!

title: Escape de la Cena Familiar
description: En el arroyo se disputa una enorme pelea con globos acuáticos, pero Craig está atrapado en la cena familiar, a menos que pueda escapar.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Origins
description: When Mom and Dad struggle to keep hyperactive, toddler-aged Gumball from trashing the house and exhausting them, they decide to buy him a pet. It works, but there's a problem: every goldfish they get him is short-lived, and inevitably ends up being flushed down the toilet.

title: 150-Piece Kit
description: Benson wants to prove that he performed a famous drum solo.

title: Bear Cleanse
description: A doctor tells the Bears to go on a cleanse to improve their health. But when Grizz realizes he can only eat what grizzly bears eat, he starts to lose his mind.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: A Little Something Between Friends
description: Pocoyo and Pato fall out - really fall out. They are so angry with each other that they build a wall between themselves. They each sit sulking on either side of the wall, until gradually they realize that it's no fun being angry with your friend, and actually they miss each other.

title: The Fly
description: Apple and Onion must rid their apartment of a fly or face eviction.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ropa Dominguera
description: JP ensucia su última ropa limpia y debe ponerse su mejor ropa de domingo para ir al arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Nom Nom's Entourage
description: Nom Nom recruits the Bears to act as his entourage of friends. But when the Bears realize Nom Nom doesn't understand friendship, they decide to kick their day of bonding into high gear.

title: #ConoceAGuepardo
description: Barbara Minerva está super celosa de la "pequeña señorita perfecta" Diana Prince. Pero cuando usa un antiguo artefacto de la colección de su padre para lanzar una maldición contra Diana, la maldición se vuelve en su contra.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Origins Part 2
description: Via the sewers, Darwin finds himself flushed out to sea. He is terrified but determined to make his way back to the Wattersons. However, a fish can't get very far on land so Darwin will have to do millions of years of evolution in a matter of hours if he's going to get home safe and sound.

title: Malgax Attacks
description: Ben finally manages to rid himself of Skurd... just when he needs the Slime-Biot most.

title: Chair
description: Unikitty finds an old, beatup recliner on the curb, but sees its inner beauty and brings it home to introduce to the gang! In a series of absurd and fun vignettes, we discover how a dirty, inanimate chair comes into each of their lives and changes them for the better. We soon learn that dear, sweet Chair was too good for this world.

title: Wednesday - Part 3
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Did Not! Did Too!
description: Bugs and Lola temporarily decide that they don't want to be friends any longer.

title: Perricornio Patinador
description: Puppycorn quiere impresionar a sus amigos patinadores con sus habilidades fantásticas, el problema es que no tiene ninguna. Con la esperanza de aumentar su confianza, Unikitty y la pandilla se ponen los trajes invisibles de la Dra. Fox para ayudarlo secretamente a realizar movimientos imposibles. Pero hacen su trabajo demasiado bien y el "patinador profesional" Puppycorn está invitado a mostrar sus habilidades en una peligrosa competencia de escenas de riesgo. ¿Hasta dónde llegará la pandilla para ayudar al cachorro a realizar sus sueños inalcanzables e increíbles?

title: Ninja vs. Lava
description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

title: Slumber Party
description: A thunderstorm forces Chloe to spend the night at the Cave with the Bears. When Chloe's parents tell the Bears to protect Chloe, they take the task a bit too seriously.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: #MeetTheCheetah
description: Barbara Minerva is super-jealous of  "little Miss Perfect" Diana Prince. But when she uses an ancient artifact from her dad's collection to place a curse on Diana, it turns out that Diana's not the one who's cursed. It's Barbara.

title: Enemy Mime
description: When the Sheriff's Dept fights a monster that copies their every move, they'll have to find a way to fight without fighting.

title: The Big Squeak
description: Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker.

title: RV Olympics
description: Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus compete in the RV Olympics.

title: The Sale
description: Gumball and Darwin are devastated to learn that Mr. Robinson, their favorite person in the world, is selling his house and leaving town. When they realize that making some final happy memories with Mr. Robinson is not enough for them, they decide to stop him leaving by sabotaging the sale.

title: Animorfosis
description: El trío Tennyson excava fósiles de dinosaurio, pero Ben no sabe que Vilgax y el Dr. Animal se complotaron para robar ADN alien del Omnitrix, pero, una vez extraído el ADN, Vilgax traiciona a su cómplice. Ahora Ben debe aliarse con el malvado doctor si quiere tener la oportunidad de derrotar al gran villano. Pero ¿puede confiar en el Dr. Animal?

title: A New Dawn
description: The Time War brings Ben, Rook, and George Washington together to battle an alien conqueror.

title: The Final Countdown
description: Rook and his little Plumbers must defend the Base from a mysterious lockdown.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Stretched Too Thin
description: After a new combo-move leaves Masko permanently limp, Axel and the team must help the fallen luchador get his stretch back.

title: Same Old World
description: Steven flies around the world.

title: Color My World
description: Pocoyo finds a new toy - a remote control that changes the colors of the things around him. It's great fun until he changes the colors of his friends. We have to help him put things back to the way they were.

title: Guy's Night
description: Pops wants to beat the milk challenge to prove he's one of the guys.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Pudding the Planet First
description: Chef accidentally cooks up a killer cyborg turkey in a failed attempt to get the kids to appreciate him on Appreciation Day.

title: You're in Control
description: When Boxman deploys a new threat, KO must turn to an old enemy for help.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: El joven y la logica
description: K.O. descubre cómo el Sr. Lógica llegó a la Plaza.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Opening Act
description: After failing to open a jar Chef believes he's past his prime and entering his twilight years. This prompts Beth and the kids to dig up something from his youth to rejuvenate him. That something turns out to be a ventriloquist dummy named Sue.

title: Belly Math
description: In order to defeat The Calculator, the Titans must learn common core math.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Sumo Goes West
description: Clarence learns his best friend Sumo may transfer to another school! It's up to Clarence to protest, petition and rally to convince everyone to let Sumo stay - or face losing his closest school pal!

title: Islands Part 5: Hide and Seek
description: While exploring some futuristic ruins, Susan sees glimpses of a familiar girl.

title: Bombazobo Vive
description: Durante un viaje de rutina al DMV, Max toma un examen de manejo para renovar su licencia. Pero cuando Zombozo, disfrazado, se apropia del papel del instructor, Ben se convierte en alienígena para detener al malvado y salvar el viaje familiar.

title: Presentando a La Creatura
description: Cuando Max se queda dormido antes de una doble función, Ben y Gwen se ven obligados a salvar el autocine solos. Ocurre que el malvado mago Hex da vida al monstruo de una película, que aterroriza a los espectadores.

title: End of an Era
description: The Time War races towards its dramatic conclusion, with the fate of the entire universe and everything in it since the very beginning of time resting in the hands of the Ben 10.

title: Los Opuestos se Atraen
description: Afirmando que es bueno de corazón, Dynamo convence a Axel y al equipo para que lo ayuden a encontrar una batería que pueda alimentar su centrífuga y liberarlo del control de Madtrap, pero Bobbie Blobby no está comprando la historia del malo.

title: #SuperWho?
description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

title: Islands Part 2: Whipple the Happy Dragon
description: Finn, Jake, and Susan set sail on a ocean voyage full of wonders and danger.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Tienes el control
description: Cuando Boxman crea una nueva amenaza, K.O. debe recurrir a un viejo enemigo para que lo ayude.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Steven Floats
description: Steven is so excited to be back home that he jumps for joy and jumps way too high.

title: Islands Part 4: Imaginary Resources
description: Finn and Jake travel to a land where reality has been redesigned and improved.

title: Serpientastrofe
description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

title: Salvajessa
description: Un encuentro con Salvajessa, guardiana de la naturaleza, inspira a Kelsey a dedicarse a una causa.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Superado
description: Cuando Rufus y Reg llegan para engañar al pueblo, el sheriff Mao Mao les enseña una lección sobre la justicia.

title: The News Never Sleeps!
description: Lil' Nelson takes a job as a paperboy, which is more difficult than it sounds in a city overrun by scorching Pyro Vipers and an evil Serpentine sorceress.

title: Tasty Heist
description: Richard's prepared one of the tastiest desserts ever, but he's locked it up tight until the friends have their boring dinner. This will not stand. Unikitty organizes a heist, assembling the friends as a crack team to get in, get out, and eat that tasty snack without Richard knowing. But this heist has hiccups. Can the friends take the cake?

title: Pocoyo's Little Friend
description: Pocoyo finds a new little friend - a very hungry caterpillar. He watches with amazement as his new friend transforms.

title: Pie Contest
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to prove to Benson that they can be judges at the pie contest.

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Instruments have been going missing from Apple and Onion's favourite music store and Chicken Nugget (who's in charge of security) doesn't want them hanging around and getting in the way.

title: Creature Feature
description: When Max dozes off before a double feature, Ben and Gwen are left to save the drive-in by themselves as the evil magician Hex brings the movie monster "That" to life, and unleashes him on the unsuspecting moviegoers.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Let's Not Be Skeletons
description: When a charismatic huckster shows up to the plaza, the product he's selling turns everything upside down.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Una Idea Huev-Xtremadamente Mala
description: Esperando "iluminar su día", Izzy y Owen decoran la silla huevo de Gwe. Pero cuando termina en un museo regentado por pollos rabiosos, deben rescatarla antes de que Gwen destruya la guardería en un berrinche de inusitada oscuridad.

title: Roller Coasting
description: Thomas wants to show Percy what it's like to ride a roller coaster, so Thomas turns the tracks of Sodor into a thrill ride.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Barn Mates
description: Steven helps two friends get along at the barn.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Baba Yaga House
description: Squatter Otter tries to win Panda's trust and convince the Bears to live in a mysterious house.

title: High Stress Express
description: During a live feed of the new transcontinental bullet train, La Grange enters the picture to outrace the train, but Ben joins in on the fun and will stop at nothing to come out on top!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: The Most Dangerous Game Show
description: Ben fights for his life on an alien reality show.

title: Bomzobo Lives
description: During a routine trip to the DMV, Max takes a driving test to renew his license, but when a disguised Zombozo hijacks the role of instructor, Ben goes alien to stop the baddie and save their family road trip.

title: Caillou's Water Park/Gone Fishing/The Water Goes 'Round/Caillou's Test Drive/A Very Good Swimmer!
description: Caillou learns that the best fun is made up and not bought and paid for./Caillou learns about patience when he goes fishing with Daddy and Grandpa at the pier./Grandma is watching Caillou for the day, and he wants her to play trucks with him./When their car breaks down, the family goes shopping for a new one./Caillou gets an introduction to what it means to be handicapped, when, at the pool, he meets Tammy.

title: No Power, No Problem!
description: When the power goes out all over Sodor, Thomas and Friends must use brain-power to navigate the island in creative new ways.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: An Egg-stremely Bad Idea
description: Hoping to 'brighten her day', Izzy and Owen pimp out Gwen's egg chair. But when it ends up in a museum run by angry chickens, they must retrieve it before Gwen destroys the daycare in a temper tantrum of unspeakable darkness.

title: Super Amazing Raft Adventure
description: Unikitty and Hawkodile are "lost at sea", stranded on a raft together. Hawkodile sees this as an opportunity to show Unikitty that he's prepared for anything with his expertly-honed survival skills, but to his shock, all of his plans keep falling apart, while Unikitty's silly "it'll all work out, let's have fun" approach is somehow working great! Will Hawkodile manage to let go of his overpreparedness to save them both, or will Unikitty whimsical fun be their doom?

title: Ejercitando los Demonios
description: Cuando una severa adicción a las pantalla convierte a los niños en holgazanes, Chef trae a una profesional para ponerlos en forma.

title: Enemigo Mimo
description: Cuando el departamento del sheriff se enfrenta a un monstruo que copia todos los movimientos, tendrán que encontrar el modo de pelear sin pelear.

title: Hide and Sneak
description: Dibble is chosen as "It" in a Whiffle game of Hide-and-Seek. The game turns serious when Bluster traps the Bears inside the Cloudseeker. Dibble and Cheer must find the Whiffles and free her friends.

title: Powerless
description: The ninja rush to the NINJAGO Museum of History to recover a dangerous scroll before it falls into the hands of the Serpentine Sorceress Aspheera.

title: Noticias de Accion
description: Dynamite Watkins llega muy lejos para anunciar una noticia.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Mystery Science Fair 201X
description: KO helps Dendy with her science fair project.

title: Boo
description: Coco shows Bing how to do really big boos, but what will happen when Bing wants to practice on Charlie?

title: The Boys Are Back in Town
description: Him brings the Rowdyruff Boys back, protecting them from the girls' feminine wiles.

title: #HateTriangle
description: When Hal's ex-girlfriend shows up at the Metropolis High homecoming game and goes love-ballistic as the villain Star Sapphire, Jessica begins to second-guess her own nonviolent tactics.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Outfoxed
description: When Rufus and Reg come to swindle the town, Sheriff Mao Mao teaches them a lesson in justice.

title: The Secret Life of Blossom Powerpuff
description: When Blossom can't join her favorite school club, she imagines what her life would be like if she joined other clubs.

title: Buggin' Out
description: When Unikitty and the gang discover a gross bug in the castle, they desperately want it gone for good, but Unikitty refuses to allow them to squish it, no matter how icky or dangerous looking it is. What sort of web is Unikitty weaving for her friends?

title: Stuck on You
description: Tired of Axel and the team taking him for granted, Masko tries to get kidnapped and ends up stuck to Dynamo, who's less than enthused with his rubbery new sidekick.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Keeping Up with the Kryptonians
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk shows Supergirl and Superman that their innate goodness might not be so pure when he takes them to a parallel world where their counterparts are impossibly aggressive and spoiled.

title: Dinosaur Day
description: Pizza Steve's jealousy ruins Uncle Grandpa's Dinosaur Day celebration for Mr. Gus.

title: Too Many Treasures
description: Hoping to fix their fort, Craig enlists the 10 Speeds to give them a ride to the legendary Junk Pile.

title: Sunday Clothes
description: JP dirties his last clean clothes and he must wear his Sunday best to the creek.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: Preparense Para Lo Peor
description: iAxel y Bobbie Blobby se saltan los simulacros de preparación para desastres de Sarge, dejando suficiente espacio en las defensas del equipo para que un cuervo se precipite y arrebata a Sarge! Sintiéndose responsable, Axel lidera al equipo en una misión de búsqueda y rescate.

title: Dragonhead
description: In desperate need of a shower due, Apple and Onion resort to desperate measures.

title: The Future
description: Steven is finally ready to move on.

title: In the Darkness/Indecisive Emily
description: An encounter with Storm and his trick rose leaves Magnus temporarily blinded and unable to brawl. With the help of an unlikely partner, Magnus pursues Storm in an attempt to defeat him and restore his vision./ Emily obtains a second Bakugan named Chrissy. It's soon obvious that Emily is having trouble brawling with both Chrissy and Webam, and it's up to Dan, Drago and Gillator to teach them how to brawl as a team.

title: Where's Gilbert?/Where I Saw it Last/Lost in the Jungle
description: Gilbert has gone missing and Caillou is very concerned./Caillou realizes that he has misplaced his new toy car./Caillou learns all about the jungle at playschool.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Go With the Flow
description: When Sal stays with Vic & Val, the boys are annoyed by him as their roommate but eventually they learn how cool and magical he is.

title: The Matchmaker
description: When Val starts a romantic match-making service, he struggles being true to his own feelings for his secret crush.

title: El Ladron de Musica
description: Manzana y Cebollín tienen que defender la tienda de música del robo de instrumentos para conseguir una llave de la tienda.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: In the Garden of Good and Eddie
description: When the girls try a quick-fix on their neglected veggie garden, they are left with a giant, mooching tomato worm they must care for.

title: Share Your Care
description: Dibble plants the seeds of a strange bush outside of its natural environment, unaware that she has unleashed a disaster: The plant multiplies and begins to quickly spread. The Bears must find a way to stop its greedy growth before it crowds out all the other plants in the Silver Lining.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Falafel en la Carcel
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben sacar a Falafel de la cárcel por un delito que no cometió.

title: La Mosca
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben deshacerse de una mosca que se metió en su apartamento o enfrentarse al desalojo.

title: One Pull Up
description: Rigby needs to do one pull-up so he can pass the park physical.

title: The Eclipse/Follow Haavik!
description: There's an eclipse happening over Los Volmos, but there's something even more strange going on. Dan and Drago quickly realize something's up; no one seems like themselves today. The two need to get to the bottom of it and return things back to normal./ Magnus and Ajit spot Haavik on the street and decide to follow him, but the shape shifting Haavik is on to them. It's not long before an epic brawl breaks out between them - Five Faction Fusion Sabrus vs. Nillious X Darkus and Pharol.

title: #SuperQuien
description: Abrumada por la cantidad de cobertura que Superman recibe en las noticias de Metrópolis, Supergirl decide mostrarle a la ciudad lo que puede hacer. Pero cuando Superman pone a todos en peligro sin querer, Supergirl debe decidir si hacer lo que es correcto para la gente o para ella misma.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Pumm-Ra
description: Mumm-Ra plans to disguise himself as a Thunderian and infiltrate Cats' Lair, but the Ancient Spirits of Evil are mad at him and won't give him any magic today. No matter, Mumm-Ra knows what a ThunderCat looks like so he slaps on some awful, unconvincing, cat make up and heads to Cats' Lair to introduce himself!

title: Sick Mao
description: When Mao Mao won't admit that he's sick, he puts the town in danger.

title: Mama Suplente
description: Cuando la mamá de Chef se convierte en maestra suplente por un día, Duncan cambia la lista de actividades de Chef por la suya.

title: Stray Bullet
description: In order to save an innocent squirrel, Bubbles gives him a dash of Chemical X, giving him some super squirrel powers.

title: Caillou's Horn/The Mighty Oak/Get Well Mr. Hinkle/The Big Boat
description: When Sarah gives Caillou an old toy horn, Caillou wants to blow it everywhere./When Mr. Hinkle has a tree cut down, Caillou is afraid his swing tree is next!/When Caillou dresses up like a mailman to deliver Mr. Hinkle's misdirected mail, he finds out Mr. Hinkle is sick./Caillou and family go on a trip on Helen's boat, an old friend of Mom's.

title: Animorphosis
description: As the Tennyson trio dig up dinosaur fossils in the Badlands, Ben is unaware that Vilgax and Dr. Amino have teamed up to steal alien DNA from within the Omnitrix, but once extracted, Vilgax double crosses his fellow villain. Ben must now join forces with the evil doctor to have a chance to defeat the big baddie, but can Dr. Amino be trusted?

title: #Beeline
description: Cuando tropieza con un malvado complot para hacer explotar un puente de la ciudad, Bumblebee se espanta y acude a sus amigas para que derroten a los malhechores. Pero cuando todas sus super amigas están ocupadas, Bumblebee debe buscar cada gramo de coraje en ella para hacer frente a la situación, a pesar de ser la más pequeña del grupo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Que no sean Esqueletos
description: Cuando un vendedor carismático llega a la Plaza, el producto que vende pone todo patas para arriba.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Kickflip McPuppycorn
description: Puppycorn wants to impress his skater friends with his sweet skills, except he has none. Hoping to boost his confidence, Unikitty and the gang put on Dr. Fox's invisibility suits to secretly help him pull off impossible moves! But they do their job too well and "pro skater" Puppycorn is invited to showcase his skills in a dangerous stunt competition. How far will the gang go to help the pup live out his rad pipe dreams?

title: La Venganza de Bao Bao
description: Cuando el antiguo compañero de Mao Mao amenaza al reino, los amigos de Mao Mao tendrán que conocer su pasado para proteger el presente.

title: Hit the Diamond
description: Steven and the Gems play an old fashioned game of baseball.

title: The Teen Titans Go Easter Holiday Classic
description: The Easter Bunny is missing, and it's up to the Titans to find him before Easter is ruined.

title: She Wore Red Velvet
description: When Booster and the JLA come under attack by a mysterious and unrelenting new villainess known as Red Velvet, Booster comes to realize she's actually the fiance he left at the altar in the future.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Pastry Peril
description: When Vic must pay off the debt he incurred at Lupe's bakery, he has no choice but to work under his rival's close supervision.

title: Islands Part 3: Mysterious Island
description: After waking up alone and shipwrecked, Finn investigates a bizarre island in search of his friends.

title: Guillermo's Gathering
description: When Vic & Val are forced to go to Guillermo's boring birthday party, they devise a scheme to leave early, but end up discovering that the party is way cooler than they thought.

title: Standards & Practices
description: The Titans' negative behavior is giving superheroes a bad name, so they must learn proper conduct to be good role models for kids.

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Clarence for President
description: It's school election time at Aberdale Elementary, and Jeff is once again determined to become Class President. However like previous years, he's unsuccessful in connecting with other kid. That is until he sees a shoe-in puppet President, the lovable Clarence!

title: All Washed Up
description: Taz decides he doesn't like taking a bath.

title: Pudin-Pocalipsis
description: Después de que Chef dice que los puntos de vista contrarios hacen al mundo más interesante y divertido, Izzy lo aplica del peor modo posible.

title: Egg Hunt
description: Robin still regrets not being able to find an Easter egg when he was a kid, so the Titans head to Gotham to solve this mystery.

title: Manzallin
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren llevarse el crédito de haber creado una nueva moda de baile.

title: Sillon
description: Unikitty encuentra una vieja silla reclinable en la acera, pero ve su belleza interior y lo lleva a casa para mostrárselo a la pandilla. En una serie de situaciones absurdas y divertidas, descubrimos cómo una silla sucia e inanimada entra en cada una de sus vidas y las cambia para mejor. Pronto aprendemos que la querida y dulce silla era demasiado buena para este mundo.

title: From Below
description: Axel juggles looking after Luka and defending the house from Dr. Nautilus's latest abomination, a tentacle monster that attacks from every drain, pipe, and faucet in the building!

title: El Ganador se lo Lleva Todo
description: Después de meses de entrenamiento para el Día del Luchador, Axel necesita que Masko lo entrene contra un par de competidores no invitados: iMadcap y Dynamo!

title: The Final Book
description: The last book of Kelsey's favorite fantasy series goes missing from the library, so Craig decides to help her solve the mystery of who took it.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: La Fiesta de Guillermo
description: Cuando Vic y Val se ven forzados a ir a la aburrida fiesta de cumpleaños de Guillermo, crean un plan para irse temprano, pero terminan descubriendo que la fiesta es mucho mejor de lo que pensaban.

title: Wildernessa
description: An encounter with Wildernessa, guardian of the wilderness, inspires Kelsey to take up a cause.

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Las Noticias Nunca Duermen
description: Lil 'Nelson toma un trabajo como repartidor de periódicos, lo cual es más difícil de lo que parece en una ciudad invadida por Pyro Vipers y una malvada hechicera serpentina.

title: Sabro Atraco
description: Richard preparó uno de los postres más sabrosos de todos los tiempos, pero lo cerró con llave hasta que los amigos terminen su cena aburrida. Esto no va a seguir así. Para organizar un atraco, Unikitty organiza a sus amigos como un comité de expertos para entrar, salir y comer ese sabroso bocadillo sin que Richard lo sepa. Pero este atraco tiene un traspié. ¿Podrán los amigos llevarse el pastel?

title: Berb-cules
description: The ThunderCats finally sit the Berbils down and tell them they really shouldn't be building things for the Mutants anymore, it's time for the Berbils to stand up for themselves. The Berbils take this advice way too far and build a giant, building-sized, Berbil named Berbcules. Berb-cules takes back everything the Berbils ever built for the Mutants and everything they ever built for the ThunderCats! Now Panthro has to figure out a way to a defeat the most powerful invention the best little builders have ever built!

title: Uncle Melvins
description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

title: Snaketastrophy
description: The Serpentine attack on NINJAGO City is seen from an unexpected perspective - entirely in the style of a live newscast delivered by Gayle Gossip and her cameraman.

title: The Show Must Go On
description: Mushpie loves to sing. The only problem is she is terrible at it! But Lilit, who has never heard her sing before, wants to make Mushpie happy and organizes a concert for her to sing in front of all the other Mushables… who are terrified at the idea! But Lilit doesn't have the heart to admit this to Mushpie.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: Pegado a Ti
description: Cansado de que Axel y el equipo lo den por sentado, Masko intenta ser secuestrado y termina atrapado en Dynamo, que está menos que entusiasmado con su nuevo compañero de goma.

title: Islands Part 1: The Invitation
description: A mysterious craft invades Ooo and Finn believes it may hold the secrets to his past.

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: Gem Drill
description: Steven takes a journey deep underground.

title: Impotente
description: El ninja corre al Museo de Historia de NINJAGO para recuperar un pergamino peligroso antes de que caiga en manos de la Hechicera Serpentina Aspheera.

title: Big Fat Alien Wedding
description: Ben and Gwen accompany Max to a wedding, which doesn't make Ben particularly happy, especially given the fact he has to wear a tux and learn how to dance. During the wedding it's revealed that the bride's parents are aliens while the groom's family are ex-Plumbers. It turns out the bride's parents are out to sabotage the wedding because of a long lasting feud with the Plumbers, and take action by demonstrating their destructive powers and causing deadly havoc. Ben, Max and Gwen enter the fray and not only save the day, but make sure the ceremony goes on as planned.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: Where I Live/A Good Friend/Just Like Me/Just In Time/Mr. Fixit
description: When an invitation for Clementine's party accidentally ends up at Sarah's, Caillou learns the differences between the addresses of the two homes./When Leo forgets his brand new toy dinosaur in the park, Daddy and Caillou go looking for it./When Clementine tells Caillou how much she likes her older brother, Billy, to teach her things, Caillou sets out to teach something to Rosie./When Caillou's dawdling causes he, Mom and Rosie to be late going to the park, they end up missing Leo./When the washing machine needs fixing, Caillou ends up helping Bob the repairman.

title: To Balderly Go
description: Prohyas is crushed when his good hair day becomes a no hair day and Vambre has to battle a furry monster alone while her bro is in shock without his locks!

title: Bao Bao's Revenge
description: When Mao Mao's old partner threatens the kingdom, his friends will need to learn about his past in order to protect the present.

title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

title: Tiko's Back?!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!
description: Tiko's Back?!: In order to make Sabrus a 6 faction fusion Bakugan, Haavik heads into the maze to try to capture a golden Bakugan who has brought "mayhem and destruction" to Earth once before - Tiko!/Arise, Ultimate Infinity!: The Awesome Brawlers manage to thwart Haavik's attempt to fuse Tiko with Sabrus, but Haavik ends up escaping with the golden Bakugan, Pyravian. Now the Awesome Brawlers must track down Haavik before he can form his ultimate 6 faction fusion Bakugan.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Jerky Jasper
description: Uncle Grandpa goes to great lengths to meet Pizza Steve's imaginary friend.

title: Kite
description: Bing and Flop are in the park to fly Bing's Hoppity Voosh kite, and Bing is excited to fly it all by himself. Will Bing be able to?

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Yard Sale
description: Each of the Bears get offbeat items at a local yard sale. Their new possessions send them on their own separate adventures.

title: The Roots
description: When Mom sees Darwin gazing longingly at a fish-tank, she thinks their mammalian lifestyle isn't fulfilling her adopted son and deep down he longs to connect with his fishy roots. So the family try to reconnect him with his aquatic culture. They try fish-food, fish-language and even fish clothes. But when none of it works, they realize they may have to let him go.

title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.

title: Bald Spot
description: Muscle Man wants to hide his bald spot at all costs.

title: Too Hot to Handle
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat.

title: Aluxes
description: Vic encuentra una antigua reliquia que invoca a una pandilla de traviesas criaturas, iy las consecuencias son desastrosas!

title: Ancient History
description: While Aspheera pursues revenge on the "Treacherous Deceiver" who betrayed her, the ninja make a startling discovery.
